{"tid":2098212,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"龍門撤出黃圈一周 大廚遭三煞伏擊  老闆：要搞就搞我","createTime":"2020-07-07T10:23:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T06:15:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e2ca6aa9c55941f7ede1679220407f10a4d90f97","tid":2098212,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T10:23:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200707/TQKUJSEKQHYAJ7FIOPOLHZDYE4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200707%2FTQKUJSEKQHYAJ7FIOPOLHZDYE4%2F&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivdOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=51b2745d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200707%2FTQKUJSEKQHYAJ7FIOPOLHZDYE4%2F&h=c4dc132c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200707/TQKUJSEKQHYAJ7FIOPOLHZDYE4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n龍門撤出黃圈一周 大廚遭三煞伏擊 <br />\n老闆：要搞就搞我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】自去年反修例運動屢遭恐嚇及破壞的知名連鎖餐廳「龍門冰室」，上周港版國安法通過後，宣佈退出黃色經濟圈，未料事隔一星期，暴力事件再升級。該餐廳一名大廚昨晨返回尖沙嘴分店開舖時，被三名男子以玻璃樽及硬物襲擊，頭破血流送院治理，兇徒逃去無蹤。冰室老闆張俊傑直斥：「你要搞就搞我！唔好搞我啲人！」慨嘆立場影響員工，對此感抱歉。有食客不齒兇徒所為，表明會繼續光顧。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/GlmjwAreskUxIcv1PZBr2ugbqKo=/640x1137/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WNH4YBXA4WZWSZKGYDFM6NUDTA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGlmjwAreskUxIcv1PZBr2ugbqKo%3D%2F640x1137%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWNH4YBXA4WZWSZKGYDFM6NUDTA.jpg&h=41915c35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n龍門冰室大廚遭人以玻璃樽及硬物施襲，頭破血流，由救護員包紮送院治理。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n現場是龍門冰室金馬倫道分店，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n馬路跑至，不斷向事主拳打腳踢並爆樽施襲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Y_7FYAEo54TrcTcRB0MrGtdhNG0=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/F6P4RFOIH7U3E4YEF2FNHF5SRQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FY_7FYAEo54TrcTcRB0MrGtdhNG0%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FF6P4RFOIH7U3E4YEF2FNHF5SRQ.jpg&h=923b2a14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張俊傑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/U5VoLlW5V2rh4OvfxVdrYbAl8yE=/640x359/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IQTIZL2U2VSZDOD7HVCVQRW5KA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FU5VoLlW5V2rh4OvfxVdrYbAl8yE%3D%2F640x359%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIQTIZL2U2VSZDOD7HVCVQRW5KA.jpg&h=d486e397&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n油尖警區刑事調查隊探員到案發現場調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早前有紋身漢「踩線」<br />\n<br />\n事發時有途人見狀爭相走避，三名兇徒犯案過程約10秒，得手後即分別向加拿分道及厚福街方向逃去，其中一人更跑往對面馬路，登上一輛接應客貨車離開。黃遇襲後頭破血流，神志迷糊，附近店舖有職員走出來協助，將他扶起坐下及報警。稍後傷者由救護員包紮送院治理。老闆張俊傑趕到醫院急症室探望夥計情況，他引述黃右邊後腦位置受傷，左手腫脹骨折，右手亦遭玻璃碎割傷。<br />\n<br />\n張續透露，前幾天已有<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n斥兇徒：「你要搞就搞我！唔好搞我啲人！」<br />\n<br />\n案發現場滿地鮮血及玻璃樽碎片，警方將案件列作傷人，交油尖警區刑事調查隊跟進，正追緝三名兇徒，其中兩人身穿黑色上衣，另一人身穿白色上衣。<br />\n<br />\n昨日下午近5時，龍門冰室在fb上載涉事閉路電視片段，指：「我夥計打999係想CALL白車，唔係叫你哋班差佬嚟煩住我做嘢，要片就喺到（度）睇」。<br />\n<br />\n事發後冰室如常營業，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n亦表明不會向惡勢力低頭，將會繼續光顧。"},{"pid":"3370564c7b2f12cf89a7b7e1fbe956d4f482ec9f","tid":2098212,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T10:25:35.000Z","msg":"搞燉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2249e4400327fa8f704f1fb6846a045db625a08","tid":2098212,"uid":57309,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T10:26:30.000Z","msg":"班pk 仲掛住內鬥"},{"pid":"4094815a379ae28d91ddb7a11ddad106b9468104","tid":2098212,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T10:26:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6ebd4dcfd8dc8da1fbb2f851b056479f2a61d647